      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new global campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand, something in the tier of Patek Philippe. i need to define our \"ideal consumer\" to make sure our creative direction is on point. can you help me build out a detailed persona? i need to know their lifestyle, interests, where they hang out, and even their typical ethnic/cultural background so we can nail the visual aesthetic and brand alignment. thanks.",
